<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-05-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-05-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="789" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d789">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">103.9169 Bogotá: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Chargé in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Daniels</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-05-16">May 16,
                                1944</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>649. From FEA, for La Spina. Embassy’s A–849, May 5. Suggest you do not
                            postpone processing of import recommendations. When possible you will be
                            informed on categories to be eliminated from decentralization, July 1,
                            1944. [FEA.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>